## Proposed Changes

### Backend Security & Schema (Phase 1)

#### [MODIFY] `backend/requirements.txt`
- Add `passlib`, `bcrypt`, `python-jose`, and `python-multipart`.

#### [MODIFY] `backend/app/models.py`
- Expand `User`: Add `email`, `hashed_password`. 
- Expand `User` for vendor attributes: Add `store_name` (String, nullable) and `is_open` (Boolean, default: False).
- Add `MenuItem` class: `id`, `vendor_id` (ForeignKey), `name`, `description`, `price` (Float), `icon` (String for Emoji).
- Update `Order`: Add `menu_item_id` (ForeignKey) for cleaner relations.

#### [MODIFY] `backend/app/schemas.py`
- Create `UserCreate`, `UserLogin`, `UserResponse`, `Token` schemas.
- Update `OrderCreate`, `OrderResponse`.
- Create `MenuItemCreate`, `MenuItemResponse`.

#### [NEW] `backend/app/utils/security.py`
- Implement password hashing verification (`context.verify`) and JWT encoding/decoding logic (`create_access_token`).

#### [NEW] `backend/app/routers/auth.py`
- Create `/register` and `/login` (returning standard `access_token`).

#### [MODIFY] `backend/app/routers/*.py`
- Add `Depends(get_current_user)` to secure the `orders` APIs.

---

### Frontend Auth & Protected Routing (Phase 2)

#### [NEW] `frontend/src/store/authStore.js`
- Create a Zustand state manager to persist the JWT token, User ID, and Role.

#### [NEW] `frontend/src/components/ProtectedRoute.jsx`
- Wrap routing components and ensure proper role-based redirection (e.g., `fan` users block-redirected from `/vendor`).

#### [NEW] `frontend/src/pages/Login.jsx` & `frontend/src/pages/Register.jsx`
- Create clean, user-friendly authentication forms with Tailwind.

#### [MODIFY] `frontend/src/App.jsx`
- Integrate `ProtectedRoute` and route mappings.

---

### Swiggy-Style Dashboards (Phase 3)

#### [MODIFY] `frontend/src/pages/FanDashboard.jsx`
- Remove the debug "Ping" buttons.
- Create dynamic Grid view mapping over backend `Vendors` (`User` table filtered by vendor role).
- Build the Menu View when selecting a vendor, displaying large emoji icons with `Add to Cart` features.

#### [MODIFY] `frontend/src/pages/VendorDashboard.jsx`
- Add UI controls to create/manage `MenuItem`s (including price and Emoji selectors).
- Connect real-time WebSocket signals for the "Order Queue" using modern "Tile" layouts.

#### [MODIFY] `frontend/src/pages/AdminDashboard.jsx`
- Populate a master table containing all Users/Vendors.

